One to One Bi Directional Mapping Using XML.


Student 	Address 

1. One Student have One address - True
2. This Address belongs to One Student - True

*************************************************

Student.java
	Address address;
<many-to-one name="address" class="Address" column="aid"/>

Address.java
	Student student;
<one-to-one name="student" class="Student"/>



Table :
ADDRESS_INFO_BI
STUDENT_INFO_BI